config ROTR_RGB_INDICATOR
	bool "ROTR per-layer RGB underglow indicator"
	depends on ZMK_RGB_UNDERGLOW
	default y
	help
	  Show the active keymap layer's colour on the underglow via a
	  layer-state-changed listener. When the underglow is toggled off it
	  stays off, except a brief fade-flash on each layer change.
